msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Loko u kume hi ndlela leyi ku fanaka e US, hi vuyelo leswaku u tirhisa "
"NOWPayments (mafungulo a ku fikelela a min. ku fana ku ya eka ndhawu ya "
"vumba). Loko u ya e US, Stripe Crypto yi tlhela yi fanaka. U nga hlayisa "
"swihlanganyelo swin'wana swo hambana naswona u laveka vuyintana bya wena ku "
"katsa."

msgid "Enabled Payment Methods"
msgstr "Swo hlayiwaka swa vuhlayi"

msgid ""
"Select which payment options will appear in your widget. Your visitors can "
"choose their preferred method."
msgstr ""
"Sakhela switirhisiwa leswi khumbulaka eka widget. Vuyintana va wena vanga va"
" katsa ndlela ya vona leyi khanyaka."

