"Stripe Crypto payments (USDC) are ONLY available for US-based businesses. If"
" you are outside the US, Stripe will only accept credit card payments to "
"your Stripe balance (not directly to crypto)."
msgstr ""
"Mufambisi wa Stripe Crypto (USDC) wu khoma hi nkarhi wa US. Loko u a swi ha "
"va e US, Stripe wu vumbuluxa tikhetho ta credit card ku tirhisa Stripe "
"balance (ku nga ri hi crypto)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"Loko u ti e US, u nga tirhisa Stripe ku tumbuluxa crypto hi ndzhaku. Loko u "
"a ti e US, hlayisa NOWPayments kumbe CoinGate ku va crypto hi ndzhaku."

