msgid ""
"A powerful, free donation and payment widget that allows your visitors to "
"support you via credit card or cryptocurrency (Quai). No monthly fees, no "
"third-party subscriptions – just your wallet and free services."
msgstr ""
"Widget ya ku tuma ndzhila ya xitshililo ni ku khoma yo kofi wo ku pfuna "
"vukonti bya wena hi khadi yo kofi kana cryptocurrency (Quai). Hi vuyelo wa "
"matsiko, hi vuyelo wa subscription ya third-party – hi wallet ya wena ni "
"xitshililo xa xiphemu."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Vhumbelo bya ku tirhisa browser yi vavala scripts ya third-party hi ku "
"tiyisa. Proxy leyi yi load scripts hi server ya wena yi ku vuyela vavala."

msgid ""
"You can update the script URLs below if the original URLs change or if you "
"want to use a different CDN."
msgstr ""
"U nga hundzuluxa URL ya script leyi, loko URL ya vumbirhi yi nyamba kumbe u "
"lave hi CDN ya vumbirhi."

